1
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:37,439
What's the rush?

2
00:01:37,439 --> 00:01:39,239
It's not gonna end that quickly.

3
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:43,959
So surprised to see me?

4
00:01:45,799 --> 00:01:47,000
You scared me to death.

5
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:49,680
How are you holding up?

6
00:01:51,079 --> 00:01:51,879
I'm fine.

7
00:01:52,439 --> 00:01:53,159
Not dead yet.

8
00:02:00,799 --> 00:02:01,959
What happened to your hand?

9
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,480
I accidentally blew my cover.

10
00:02:06,359 --> 00:02:07,640
The Master found out I was helping you.

11
00:02:14,199 --> 00:02:15,159
What are you doing?

12
00:02:15,159 --> 00:02:16,599
The Master suspects you betrayed Wujie.

13
00:02:16,599 --> 00:02:17,879
He ordered me to take your life.

14
00:02:17,879 --> 00:02:19,599
If you return and accept punishment,

15
00:02:19,599 --> 00:02:20,680
I'll plead your case.

16
00:02:25,759 --> 00:02:26,879
You always show up covered in wounds.

17
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:28,719
Out with it.

18
00:02:29,639 --> 00:02:31,159
What do you need my help with this time?

19
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:35,599
Don't worry.

20
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,560
What about Youying?

21
00:02:45,879 --> 00:02:47,400
Still no match for me.

22
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,520
I'll stay hidden in the shadows for now.

23
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:15,680
Take care of yourself.

24
00:03:22,159 --> 00:03:22,840
This is for you.

25
00:03:24,159 --> 00:03:24,840
I'm leaving.

26
00:03:32,319 --> 00:03:33,080
What was that...

27
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:36,240
Why does she always leave through the back door?

28
00:03:57,319 --> 00:03:58,599
Idiot.

29
00:03:58,599 --> 00:03:59,840
How could you be so reckless?

30
00:04:00,919 --> 00:04:01,759
Dad.

31
00:04:03,159 --> 00:04:04,599
Do you think he'll go and report me?

32
00:04:05,639 --> 00:04:05,960
Well...

33
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:07,639
That Ye Qingxue was there too.

34
00:04:07,639 --> 00:04:09,680
What if she speaks up? What do we do?

35
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:10,240
Hurry, think.

36
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,199
Come up with something.

37
00:04:13,199 --> 00:04:16,000
This Ye Qingxue isn't someone we can handle.

38
00:04:25,319 --> 00:04:26,279
In-law.

39
00:04:26,279 --> 00:04:27,639
Let me tell you.

40
00:04:27,639 --> 00:04:28,839
That kid Yang Yunfan,

41
00:04:28,839 --> 00:04:31,560
has been with Ye Qingxue every day lately.

42
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:32,240
He's hard to deal with.

43
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:35,759
We need to get the Zhenhai Calming Manual.

44
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:38,040
Don't you think we could just

45
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,040
get rid of them outright?

46
00:04:39,959 --> 00:04:42,399
I secured the Zhenhai Calming Manual.

47
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:44,279
I caught that kid today.

48
00:04:44,279 --> 00:04:45,439
You don't need to worry about it anymore.

49
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:48,519
That's great news.

50
00:04:48,519 --> 00:04:50,079
So my son-in-law's illness

51
00:04:50,079 --> 00:04:51,560
can be kept under control for now.

52
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:53,839
But I'm worried

53
00:04:53,839 --> 00:04:55,800
that kid Yang Yunfan

54
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:58,959
will still get in the way of our bigger plans.

55
00:04:58,959 --> 00:05:00,399
So,

56
00:05:00,399 --> 00:05:02,800
why not take this chance

57
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:04,120
to get rid of him?

58
00:05:06,319 --> 00:05:07,560
Just be smart about it.

59
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:08,399
Alright.

60
00:05:08,759 --> 00:05:09,560
Don't worry, in-law.

61
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,240
Then it's settled.

62
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:10,839
Good.

63
00:05:13,279 --> 00:05:14,079
Pen and paper.

64
00:05:24,279 --> 00:05:26,079
Mingcheng.

65
00:05:26,079 --> 00:05:28,199
Go find the person on this paper to get the medicine.

66
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,439
Listen to me carefully.

67
00:05:30,439 --> 00:05:32,439
Tomorrow, before the assessment,

68
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:34,240
swap out all of Yang Yunfan's herbs

69
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,639
with this batch.

70
00:05:36,319 --> 00:05:36,959
Understood?

71
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,439
Understood.

72
00:05:47,839 --> 00:05:49,160
Everyone.

73
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:51,639
Today is the Second Trial of the Five Elements,

74
00:05:51,639 --> 00:05:53,240
the Earth Element Examination.

75
00:05:54,079 --> 00:05:55,680
The five elements unite as one,

76
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:57,160
all things return to their source.

77
00:05:57,160 --> 00:05:59,839
The theme is strengthening the foundation.

78
00:05:59,839 --> 00:06:01,319
This is the focus of the assessment.

79
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:04,319
Our professional judges

80
00:06:04,319 --> 00:06:05,240
will evaluate all of you.

81
00:06:06,439 --> 00:06:08,639
This not only tests your skills,

82
00:06:08,639 --> 00:06:09,600
but more importantly,

83
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:12,319
it tests your hearts as physicians.

84
00:06:12,959 --> 00:06:14,639
I really didn't expect

85
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:17,040
to be grouped with you.

86
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:19,800
Could it be that the heavens

87
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:21,959
want your departure

88
00:06:21,959 --> 00:06:23,720
to be even more tragic?

89
00:06:30,399 --> 00:06:31,839
Sorry, Li Xiangyang.

90
00:06:31,839 --> 00:06:33,519
Your description is so vivid and cute.

91
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:36,120
Did you secretly practice that at home?

92
00:06:36,639 --> 00:06:37,240
Don't worry,

93
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,639
when you're coughing up blood later,

94
00:06:38,639 --> 00:06:40,240
don't use your kiddie watch to call Daddy.

95
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,360
You...

96
00:06:50,319 --> 00:06:52,680
It seems the atmosphere

97
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:54,279
of this assessment is quite tense.

98
00:06:54,279 --> 00:06:56,079
Now, please, everyone,

99
00:06:56,079 --> 00:06:56,759
take your positions.

100
00:06:58,839 --> 00:07:01,079
This is the only match left

101
00:07:01,079 --> 00:07:02,120
for you to act all cocky.

102
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:04,279
Good luck.

103
00:07:04,279 --> 00:07:05,279
Just you wait.

104
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:07,000
Please.

105
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,839
I now declare

106
00:07:10,839 --> 00:07:12,439
the competition open.

107
00:07:12,439 --> 00:07:13,839
Distribute the herbs to everyone.

108
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,199
Come here.

109
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:23,000
Give it to me.

110
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:23,959
Get lost!

111
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:09,759
"The medicine has been tampered with."

112
00:08:24,759 --> 00:08:25,639
These herbs...

113
00:08:39,039 --> 00:08:40,840
They really were targeting me.

114
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,519
There's something wrong with my herbs.

115
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:11,320
I request to halt the trial immediately.

116
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:12,159
And replace the herbs.

117
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:26,440
I've inspected all these herbs myself.

118
00:09:27,559 --> 00:09:28,600
There's nothing wrong with them.

119
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:31,399
Aren't you just a little too nervous?

120
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:33,440
Yang Yunfan.

121
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:36,559
Are you afraid you're going to lose?

122
00:09:36,919 --> 00:09:38,639
So you're making excuses ahead of time?

123
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:40,320
Young Master Yang.

124
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:42,080
You claim there's an issue with these herbs.

125
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:43,120
Do you have any proof?

126
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:44,240
Pharmacy Master Lu.

127
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:47,120
Drinking this is no laughing matter.

128
00:09:47,679 --> 00:09:48,919
If you have no evidence,

129
00:09:48,919 --> 00:09:50,039
don't go throwing accusations around.

130
00:09:50,039 --> 00:09:51,879
I'm not going to halt the trial

131
00:09:51,879 --> 00:09:53,039
based on your baseless guesses.

132
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:01,720
I believe him.

133
00:10:14,879 --> 00:10:17,279
I request a re-inspection of the herbs.

134
00:10:17,279 --> 00:10:19,039
Even if it's just a formality.

135
00:10:21,159 --> 00:10:21,960
Young Lady Ye.

136
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:25,120
Out of respect for your contributions

137
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:26,639
that I let you enter the inner arena.

138
00:10:26,639 --> 00:10:28,559
If you keep making a scene,

139
00:10:28,559 --> 00:10:31,679
questioning Mystic Water Hall's herbs,

140
00:10:31,679 --> 00:10:32,879
then I'm sorry,

141
00:10:32,879 --> 00:10:34,360
but I'll have to clear the arena.

142
00:10:38,639 --> 00:10:41,279
Besides, the growing and storage of herbs

143
00:10:41,279 --> 00:10:43,399
is Green Wood Hall's responsibility.

144
00:10:49,879 --> 00:10:51,120
And as for you,

145
00:10:51,120 --> 00:10:52,399
if you have no proof,

146
00:10:52,399 --> 00:10:53,840
then get back there and compete properly.

147
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:56,200
Otherwise, I'll disqualify you.

148
00:10:57,799 --> 00:10:59,120
So, the contest...

149
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:00,120
Are you in or not?

150
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:00,919
I'm in.

151
00:11:07,679 --> 00:11:09,679
Good. The contest will continue.

152
00:11:49,279 --> 00:11:50,279
Well-balanced blend,

153
00:11:50,879 --> 00:11:51,799
and precise heat control.

154
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:58,639
Just as expected from Li Chiyao.

155
00:11:58,639 --> 00:12:00,240
You're getting more masterful by the day.

156
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:01,399
It seems

157
00:12:01,399 --> 00:12:03,600
this trial should be no problem for you.

158
00:12:17,679 --> 00:12:19,480
What's wrong, Yang Yunfan?

159
00:12:20,519 --> 00:12:21,960
Still not finished?

160
00:12:22,919 --> 00:12:24,360
Are you brewing medicine,

161
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:26,240
or just pulling an all-nighter?

162
00:12:28,039 --> 00:12:29,440
If you can't do it, just go home,

163
00:12:42,879 --> 00:12:44,120
you little schoolboy.

164
00:13:03,919 --> 00:13:05,679
Excellent technique.

165
00:13:14,159 --> 00:13:14,960
Pharmacy Master Lu.

166
00:13:16,240 --> 00:13:17,840
Drink up.

167
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:19,720
Cold medicine loses its potency.

168
00:13:25,799 --> 00:13:26,799
It's fine, just a bit hot.

169
00:13:26,799 --> 00:13:28,840
I'll finish Li Chiyao's first.

170
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:33,000
Deputy Chief Pharmacist Cheng, you first.

171
00:13:47,399 --> 00:13:48,759
What's wrong with Deputy Chief Pharmacist Cheng?

172
00:13:54,519 --> 00:13:55,519
This...

173
00:13:58,440 --> 00:13:59,360
Yang Yunfan!

174
00:13:59,360 --> 00:14:00,600
What did you do to the medicine?

175
00:14:01,240 --> 00:14:03,639
How dare you poison a judge mid-exam!

176
00:14:04,480 --> 00:14:05,639
You can't blame me for this.

177
00:14:05,639 --> 00:14:07,279
I said before the contest started,

178
00:14:07,279 --> 00:14:08,519
the herbs had serious problems.

179
00:14:08,519 --> 00:14:09,600
But you insisted I proceed anyway.

180
00:14:09,600 --> 00:14:10,720
Now that someone's hurt,

181
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:12,960
shouldn't you, Lu Daozai, take the blame?

182
00:14:12,960 --> 00:14:14,039
How dare you!

183
00:14:14,039 --> 00:14:15,879
You clearly knew the herbs were tainted,

184
00:14:15,879 --> 00:14:16,720
yet still gave them to a judge.

185
00:14:16,720 --> 00:14:18,120
That's even more unforgivable.

186
00:14:18,120 --> 00:14:19,399
My herbs have a problem,

187
00:14:19,399 --> 00:14:20,320
so why are you so excited?

188
00:14:21,600 --> 00:14:22,639
Do you really have something to hide?

189
00:14:22,639 --> 00:14:23,240
You...

190
00:14:25,039 --> 00:14:26,279
Don't be in such a rush.

191
00:14:27,120 --> 00:14:29,240
Let me show you all another little trick.

192
00:14:45,159 --> 00:14:46,080
Spirits of heaven, spirits of earth

193
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:53,720
Rise!

194
00:14:59,279 --> 00:15:00,120
What the heck?

195
00:15:04,960 --> 00:15:06,039
You're fine?

196
00:15:07,240 --> 00:15:08,240
Was something supposed to happen?

197
00:15:29,519 --> 00:15:31,039
Deputy Chief Pharmacist Cheng, after you.

198
00:15:34,200 --> 00:15:34,840
Deputy Chief Pharmacist Cheng.

199
00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:36,279
Yang Yunfan.

200
00:15:39,440 --> 00:15:40,200
You...

201
00:15:44,159 --> 00:15:45,320
My assistant,

202
00:15:45,320 --> 00:15:46,639
Gu Ruoqiu,

203
00:15:46,639 --> 00:15:48,039
saw Lu Mingcheng

204
00:15:48,039 --> 00:15:49,600
swap out Yang Yunfan's batch of herbs.

205
00:15:52,080 --> 00:15:53,600
Yes, I saw it with my own eyes.

206
00:15:54,440 --> 00:15:55,159
Come here.

207
00:15:56,480 --> 00:15:57,480
Hand it over.

208
00:15:57,480 --> 00:15:58,279
Get lost!

209
00:16:07,440 --> 00:16:09,480
I didn't do it!

210
00:16:09,480 --> 00:16:10,240
I...

211
00:16:12,440 --> 00:16:13,200
Guards!

212
00:16:19,679 --> 00:16:20,080
I...

213
00:16:20,080 --> 00:16:21,320
I'm the Young Master of the Lu Family.

214
00:16:21,320 --> 00:16:23,039
I'm to inherit Mystic Water Hall someday.

215
00:16:23,039 --> 00:16:24,120
How dare you lay a hand on me?

216
00:16:25,159 --> 00:16:26,000
Get out of my way!

217
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:29,720
Lu Mingcheng,

218
00:16:29,720 --> 00:16:32,120
Are you still holding a grudge

219
00:16:32,519 --> 00:16:33,799
because you lost to Yang Yunfan?

220
00:16:36,080 --> 00:16:36,840
That's what I was thinking.

221
00:16:37,279 --> 00:16:38,519
He obviously has a nasty temper.

222
00:16:40,399 --> 00:16:41,240
Everyone,

223
00:16:41,759 --> 00:16:44,440
the way I see this matter,

224
00:16:44,440 --> 00:16:47,200
someone is secretly lining their pockets,

225
00:16:47,200 --> 00:16:48,879
using inferior goods,

226
00:16:48,879 --> 00:16:51,320
to corrupt this exam's integrity,

227
00:16:51,320 --> 00:16:52,720
and to frame my son.

228
00:16:53,120 --> 00:16:54,360
But rest assured, everyone,

229
00:16:54,639 --> 00:16:57,480
Mystic Water Hall will fully investigate

230
00:16:57,480 --> 00:16:59,480
and give everyone a satisfactory answer, all right?

231
00:17:02,360 --> 00:17:04,359
You sure know how to dodge responsibility.

232
00:17:04,359 --> 00:17:06,720
Trying to clear your son with a few words?

233
00:17:07,279 --> 00:17:08,839
Since we have a witness,

234
00:17:08,839 --> 00:17:10,400
the investigation begins with him.

235
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:12,680
Dad, save me!

236
00:17:13,400 --> 00:17:13,839
Save me!

237
00:17:13,839 --> 00:17:17,079
Lu Mingcheng attempted to sabotage the Pharmacist Trial.

238
00:17:17,079 --> 00:17:18,240
The evidence is conclusive.

239
00:17:18,240 --> 00:17:19,039
Take him away at once.

240
00:17:19,519 --> 00:17:20,759
No!

241
00:17:20,759 --> 00:17:21,480
What do you think you're doing?

242
00:17:21,480 --> 00:17:22,039
Let go of me!

243
00:17:23,559 --> 00:17:25,000
Lu Mingcheng's case

244
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:26,680
will be fully investigated

245
00:17:26,680 --> 00:17:28,200
by the Mystic Medicine Association Committee.

246
00:17:28,200 --> 00:17:29,480
No need to trouble you, Young Lady Ye.

247
00:17:31,839 --> 00:17:33,680
Everyone saw that, didn't they?

248
00:17:33,680 --> 00:17:36,119
Lu Daozai won't let us take Lu Mingcheng.

249
00:17:37,079 --> 00:17:38,519
Could it be that the swapped herbs

250
00:17:38,519 --> 00:17:40,279
were prepared by Pharmacy Master Lu?

251
00:17:40,279 --> 00:17:42,440
You're just a spoiled heir.

252
00:17:42,440 --> 00:17:44,920
Where would you get so many tainted herbs?

253
00:17:44,920 --> 00:17:46,440
You're slandering me!

254
00:17:47,160 --> 00:17:48,880
You're clearly framing the Lu Family,

255
00:17:48,880 --> 00:17:51,559
trying to wipe out the entire Lu Family!

256
00:17:51,559 --> 00:17:54,440
Pharmacy Master Lu, it's just a suspicion.

257
00:17:58,240 --> 00:18:00,160
No evidence points to Pharmacy Master Lu.

258
00:18:00,960 --> 00:18:03,720
Miss Ye, no need to overreact.

259
00:18:04,480 --> 00:18:06,680
The Mystic Medicine Association isn't yours alone.

260
00:18:07,480 --> 00:18:09,519
Best leave it to the committee to decide.

261
00:18:11,839 --> 00:18:12,640
Fine.

262
00:18:13,119 --> 00:18:15,039
I'd like to see

263
00:18:15,039 --> 00:18:16,720
what kind of answer you'll come up with.

264
00:18:17,119 --> 00:18:18,079
Take him away.

265
00:18:21,160 --> 00:18:21,759
I can walk on my own.

266
00:18:21,759 --> 00:18:22,799
Move aside.

267
00:18:23,519 --> 00:18:24,319
Don't worry.

268
00:18:24,319 --> 00:18:24,920
It'll be fine.

269
00:18:37,240 --> 00:18:39,640
Since everything has been cleared up,

270
00:18:39,640 --> 00:18:42,200
congrats to Yang Yunfan on advancing.
